source:
TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_SEQ_00<tab>Chaqurl Qhotl would persuade you of the truth of his theory regarding the fate of the mysterious race of catfish people.
※The difficulty of this quest will be synced to your current level.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>Règle spéciale<var 1D /var>:  synchronisation de quête avec limitation de job ou de classe<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>

Chaqurl Qhotl est persuadé que lors des temps difficiles, ses ancêtres n'ont pas hésité à partager leurs ressources avec les mystérieux hommes-poissons-chats.

source:
TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_SEQ_01<tab>Convinced of the merits of Chaqurl Qhotl's argument, you express your support for his theory that the Qitari sought to share their food supply with the suffering catfish people, before the latter tribe's unfortunate disappearance from the forest. Grudgingly agreeing that his son may have a point, the stubborn Qitari agrees to assist in the restoration of the third stela.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_SEQ_01<tab>* <var 1A 02 /var>Cette quête est <var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> synchronisée<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> avec votre niveau.<var 1A 01 /var>
* <var 1A 02 /var>Il n'est possible de progresser dans cette quête qu'avec la classe ou le job qui a servi à la commencer.<var 1A 01 /var> 

Vous avez fait savoir à Chaqurl Qhotl que vous partagiez son opinion. La restauration de la stèle va pouvoir commencer sous vos yeux. Parlez à Chaqurl Qhotl lorsque vous souhaiterez que les Qitari se mettent à l'ouvrage.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_SEQ_02<tab>Under your watchful eye, the Qitari artisans restore the third stela to Chaqurl Qhotl's best interpretation of its former glory. Encouraged and heartened by reclaiming yet another vital piece of their legacy, the Stewards now pursue their excavation efforts with newfound zeal. Continue to lend them your aid in their efforts should you so desire.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_SEQ_02<tab>Les Qitari du plateau de Hopl célèbrent la restauration de la troisième stèle légendaire. Mais les fouilles ne sont pas terminées pour autant<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_CHAQURLQHOTL_000_001<tab>Father may interpret the markings differently, but I am certain that my ancestors were not so cruel and violent as he would say. When famine struck the forest, we Qitari took pity on the catfish people, and shared with them our freshest catches!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_CHAQURLQHOTL_000_001<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> souuutenir théorie de Chaqurl Qhotl<var 1D /var>? <var 08 E905 ((Amie)) ((Ami)) /var> aussi penser que Qitari partager nourriture avec gentils hommes-poissons-chats<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_CHAQURLQHOTL_000_002<tab>That they vanished from the Greatwood after this is a pity, but I know that our forefathers did all they could to save their slippery little friends. This is most definitely, most in-<var 1A 02 /var>tubit<var 1A 01 /var>-ably the case, do you not agree?
target: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_CHAQURLQHOTL_000_002<tab>Quand famine frapper forêt, il y a longtemps, Qitari vouloir aider autres peuples. Chaqurl Qhotl être sûûûr<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_SYSTEM_000_003<tab>If you vouch for Chaqurl Qhotl's theory, the third stela will be restored to reflect his interpretation of history. Proceed, and you will be unable to view the stela as Qitarl Natl envisions it.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_SYSTEM_000_003<tab>Si vous choisissez de soutenir la théorie de Chaqurl Qhotl, la stèle des Qitari sera restaurée selon cette hypothèse. Vous ne pourrez pas voir la version proposée par Qitarl Natl.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_SYSTEM_000_004<tab>The rewards you receive and the content of the quests to follow will be the same regardless of the choice you make. You are free to choose the version of history you find most compelling.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_SYSTEM_000_004<tab>Les récompenses que vous obtiendrez seront les mêmes dans les deux cas. Suivez donc vos convictions pour faire ce choix.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_Q1_000_000<tab>Lend your support to Chaqurl Qhotl's theory?
target: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_Q1_000_000<tab>Souhaitez-vous soutenir la théorie de Chaqurl Qhotl et poursuivre l'histoire des Qitari<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_CHAQURLQHOTL_000_006<tab>Mag-<var 1A 02 /var>fin<var 1A 01 /var>-icent! I knew we shared a like mind, you and I.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_CHAQURLQHOTL_000_006<tab>Waaah<var 1D /var>! Si <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> être d'accord avec Chaqurl Qhotl alors théorie forcément correcte<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_QITARLNATL_000_006<tab>Perhaps the boy is right, and history is at times not so cruel as it may seem at a glance. In any event, if you truly find his version of events more compelling, I see no reason to object.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_QITARLNATL_000_006<tab>Père être très fier de fils... Qitarl Natl aussi aider à restaurer stèle<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_CHAQURLQHOTL_000_007<tab>Spli-<var 1A 02 /var>fen<var 1A 01 /var>-derous! And with that, let's get the restoration of the third stela started! You'll stick around to see that everything is done right, won't you? Whenever you are ready to begin, just say the word!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_CHAQURLQHOTL_000_007<tab>Enfin Qitari pouuuvoir faire revivre grande stèle des ancêtres<var 1D /var>! Chaqurl Qhotl vouloir que <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> voir résultat en premier, alors parler à Chaqurl Qhotl pour commencer restauration.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ042_03805_CHAQURLQHOTL_000_008<tab>Are you ready, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>? Then Father and I shall call for our best artisans at once!
